Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.70,0:02:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同学们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,课本上的点与点连好了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样由三条直线围成的叫三角形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而由四条直线围成的则是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.20,0:02:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柴田同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.10,0:02:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.30,0:02:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了 爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.90,0:02:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平时一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.00,0:02:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的眼神都很悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.30,0:02:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱 你又在烦恼了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.30,0:03:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}死胡同的对面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是地狱少女那里看到的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是下一个下地狱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.60,0:03:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她要告诉你这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.80,0:03:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在公园的哪里上吊的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.60,0:03:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,云梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,云梯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.10,0:03:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.00,0:04:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 云梯 云梯啊 是云梯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 啊 这个这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,松野边镇员工神秘自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.20,0:04:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是那里的镇长吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.30,0:04:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人也在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.10,0:04:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一看就像是做了坏事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自杀了的桐野家族成员怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.50,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一个上高中的女儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.30,0:04:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妻子十多年前就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里的事情好像都是女儿在干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.30,0:04:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇长在工作上名声相当不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他那当助手的儿子有许多不好的传言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.70,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵苑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.00,0:05:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话 现在的话还可以原谅你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去自首吧 把真相说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少可以保住性命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.30,0:05:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.80,0:05:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你爸爸死得那么惨才特别照顾你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞清楚自己的立场啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.90,0:05:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.70,0:05:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.50,0:05:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我借的钱就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.90,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请 请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.50,0:06:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.60,0:06:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.60,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它忘掉 明白吗 我出去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 这么晚了你去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请您确认遗体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从解剖结果来看 应该是自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.40,0:06:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,信封呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.30,0:06:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大约这么大的 应该带着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.90,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.80,0:06:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 什么也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.00,0:07:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请节哀顺便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.50,0:07:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您没有必要出席追悼会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不能出席呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.40,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问问自己的良心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也太没礼貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.00,0:07:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,义行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来你对我有些误解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.40,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没装傻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.40,0:07:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.90,0:07:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是误解 交给警方调查吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天请您回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.40,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 太没礼貌了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.40,0:07:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇长为职员的死感到悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从繁忙的公务中抽出空来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.20,0:07:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这里出席追悼会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然叫他回去 真是太…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.80,0:07:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.10,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我确实看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.40,0:08:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使你说看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有证据我们没办法调查啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.90,0:08:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被他们销毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你适可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.80,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楠木镇长怎么可能做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要钱的话有很多更好的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.50,0:08:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}有其父必有其女 把自杀怪别人 是想要钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}向镇长道歉    滚出镇子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.00,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.10,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐野小姐 打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.30,0:09:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问是哪位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是杂志社的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.70,0:09:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对媒体已经说了很多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没有认真对待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有人写了完全相反的内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.30,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇长级别的丑闻啊很难处理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.60,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人死了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很多地方都登了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是被杀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有证据就没有说服力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.40,0:09:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一点你应该也明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.70,0:09:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜访你之前我向当地人打听了不少事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.20,0:09:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没有人说楠木的坏话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.10,0:10:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常热心 致力于福利事业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对此处的敬老院也有高额捐款
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楠木 他儿子义行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和黑社会的人在一起的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.30,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要将此事公开的爸爸死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.00,0:10:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片也不知去向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是会自杀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.20,0:10:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想也觉得奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是全部经过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人怎么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.90,0:10:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只相信自己看到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.50,0:10:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.40,0:10:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您还是帮我写吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.00,0:10:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请报道楠木一事尚有悬疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.80,0:10:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有确凿证据的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界上是有规则的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.30,0:11:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保护杀人犯的规则吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种规则的话 没有必要去遵守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.20,0:11:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和地狱少女见过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.50,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见过吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.90,0:11:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放弃掉吧 报仇这事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之希望你放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要听你的教训
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我些时间可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会试着调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.20,0:11:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你能不能满意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会试着得出结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看了那个再做决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有什么目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得报了仇只会感到空虚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请允许我单刀直入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.60,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐野先生的死因不是自杀吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.30,0:12:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白您为什么会这样问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.00,0:12:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为桐野先生的女儿这样告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.20,0:12:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可就为难了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然相信这种毫无根据的谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.80,0:12:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也没有证据证明它是谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.60,0:12:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.10,0:12:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是想知道真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是怎样的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想找到能让自己信服的答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.30,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不用再谈下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请让我见镇长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.10,0:12:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和他谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.40,0:12:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在吧 能听见吧楠木先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 区区自由撰稿人好大的口气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才能当自由撰稿人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,义行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:13:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我双亲早亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是祖母抚养我长大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.70,0:13:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还没好好报答她就去世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.40,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以一看到老人总是心怀愧疚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我自己也是老人了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉 工作堆了好多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.00,0:13:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谷本太太 您的腰好些了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.70,0:13:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能不要紧 我已经不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您这样子 精神还是不错的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上任院长死去后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的土地和建筑物所有权证书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.80,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都落到黑社会的人手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们计划在这里建设高级公寓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.30,0:13:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那样的话老人们就无家可归了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我恳求他们终止计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.80,0:13:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在其他方面给黑社会行方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.70,0:14:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐野察觉了这一点向我们勒索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.70,0:14:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不可能向这种卑鄙的人妥协
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然拒绝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能他欠债了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.50,0:14:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙明白了不可能拿到钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.30,0:14:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就自杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.70,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.00,0:14:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说想供女儿上东京的大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的男人怎么会自杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.00,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您明白自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.80,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有下手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但肯定是有人为了我而下的手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,写不写由你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可如果我垮了这里就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.70,0:14:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是这里倒闭了会怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住在这里的老人们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天大概就这些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果你爸爸的死因还是没弄清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.80,0:15:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我会再去和楠木谈谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.00,0:15:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 世上有些事情是无法分清楚善恶的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.30,0:15:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这个事件也许就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 请放弃报仇吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.20,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然雇用那种笔杆流氓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道你在想什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.00,0:16:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过就这样两清了如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.30,0:16:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇长变得很沮丧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.80,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再令他苦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能说出这么傲慢的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傲慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.10,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傲慢的是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是爸爸垮台了你知道会怎样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.30,0:16:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多人会遇到困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.10,0:16:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你爸爸死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你一个人流泪而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.70,0:16:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只为自己的感情就要毁了这个镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也该醒悟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇里的人对你生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不是不讲理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会写的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.90,0:16:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我会藏在心底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.90,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有一事相求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.50,0:16:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你向桐野先生的女儿低头认错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向她磕头认错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也快上大学了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.90,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么上班 结婚 都是一眨眼的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须更加努力工作才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不给你准备一套嫁妆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是会让你难堪的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 工作了 工作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.20,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我答应那女孩要得出结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.90,0:17:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能想到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.90,0:17:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有求您做这件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.80,0:17:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经只剩下你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸就只有你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.50,0:18:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能听这种人说的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.40,0:18:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他以后肯定会勒索钱财
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.00,0:18:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是桐野不对还是你不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.60,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我敢说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桐野的女儿的心是纯粹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你被玷污的儿子不同 是纯粹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.40,0:18:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.80,0:18:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我作为一个父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很羡慕拥有这样的女儿的桐野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.30,0:18:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么无聊的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.70,0:18:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以桐野沙树小姐的名义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您父亲开设了一个帐户
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.50,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本放在鄙行的出租保险箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于合同期已满 所以交给您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.50,0:19:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果您能够继续存下去的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.00,0:19:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么拼命地工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.00,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果只留下这么点钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪想敲诈别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.00,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果死得那么惨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是说他倒霉 还是说他可怜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是柴田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.60,0:19:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在带楠木去你那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.70,0:19:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让他向你谢罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.90,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.10,0:19:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.30,0:19:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经无所谓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.60,0:20:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经想清楚应该怎么做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你决定放弃报仇了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.30,0:20:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸是无可代替的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.80,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管他做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.50,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说都是个慈祥的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那帮人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.00,0:20:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.20,0:20:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个镇子怎么样和我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.90,0:20:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能为爸爸做的就只有这个了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.10,0:20:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.80,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.70,0:20:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.50,0:21:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 爸爸他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.80,0:21:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送你前往地狱的小船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.00,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.20,0:21:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 是那个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子把我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.70,0:21:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让我向那个孩子道个歉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.90,0:21:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无能为力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.10,0:21:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为无论自己何时死去都不会有遗恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.10,0:21:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来还是留下了一件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.50,0:21:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.90,0:22:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,楠木亮造 松野边镇镇长失踪事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.50,0:22:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今已经过了一周
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.80,0:22:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行踪仍未明了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.50,0:22:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.70,0:22:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.60,0:22:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是做了坏事的人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.10,0:22:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不好吗
